quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  23,93,"Vuga uti:- Muremyi wanje, iyo unyereka ibihano vyabo wemereye mubantu babi"
  23,94,"Muremyi wanje, ntunshire mu bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  23,95,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe mukukwereka ivyo twabemereye, turafise ubushobozi bwavyo"
  23,96,"Nukure ibintu bibi mukuriha ibikorwa vyiza, kuko twebwe turafise ubumenyi bw’ivyo bavuga vyose"
  23,97,"Kandi uvuge uti:- Muremyi wanje, ndikinze kuri wewe kubera amosha mabi y’amashetani"
  23,98,Kandi ndikinze kuri wewe Muremyi wanje kugira ngo ntibanyice
  23,99,"Kugeza aho umwe muribo ashikirwa n’urupfu akavuga ati :- Muremyi wanje, nunsubize kw’Isi"
  23,100,"Kugira ngo nkore ibikorwa vyiza vy’ubu, aho gukora ivyo nasigaje inyuma, oya ! mu vy’ukuri iri n’ijambo gusa uvuga kubwawe n’imbere yabo hariho ubundi buzima inyuma y’urupfu kugeza k’umusi wukuzurwa kw’abantu"
  23,101,"Mugihe hazovuzwa inzamba, aho niho hatazoba ubucuti hagati yabo kuri uwo musi kandi ntawuzobaza uwundi"
  23,102,"Nayo bamwe hazoba kuminzani y’ibikorwa vyabo biremereye, abo nibo bene intsinzi nyakuri"
  23,103,Nayo abazoba bafise kuminzani yabo ihoyahoya abo bantu nibo bataye imitima yabo muruhombo n’ubwicaro bwabo nubwo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  23,104,Uwo muriro uzobabura amaso yabo nabo bazoba bari muriwo bahekenya amenyo yabo kubera ibihano bikaze cane
  23,105,Mbega ntamajambo yanje mwamye musomerwa namwe mugaca muyahakana
  23,106,"Bavuze bati :- Muremyi wacu, twebwe twararengewe n’amabi yacu nukuba mubantu batakaye"
  23,107,"Muremyi wacu, nudukure muri uwu muriro udahera, nitwasubira kugira ibindi bicumuro tuzoba twarahemukiye imitima yacu"
  23,108,"Imana ivuga iti:- nimugume muriwo kandi ntimumvugishe"
  23,109,"Ntankeka hari umurwi w’abantu banje wavuga uti :- Muremyi wacu twebwe turemeye mugabo nutugirire ikigongwe n’Impuhwe zawe, kuko ari wewe mwiza w’impuhwe zose"
  23,110,Mugabo mwebwe mwaraba jajuriyeko kugeza naho babibagiza kunyibuka kandi mwahora mubatwenga
  23,111,"Mu vy’ukuri uno musi ndabahemvye Ijuru kubera ukwihangana kwanyu, kandi ntankeka abo bantu nibo bene intsinzi"
  23,112,"Imana izovumera iti:- mbega mwabaye kw’Isi imisi ingana gute muharuye kurugero rw’imyaka"
  23,113,"Bazokwishura bati:- twebwe twicaye ngaha kw’Isi umusi umwe gusa canke igice cawo, rero nimubabaze abagira ibiharuro"
  23,114,"Izobishura iti:- mwebwe ntimwabaye kw’Isi atari ikiringo kigufiya gusa iyo muba mubizi"
  23,115,Mbega mwiyumviriye yuko twabaremeye ubusa yuko mutazosubizwa iwacu
  23,116,"Haninahazwa Imana Umwami w’ukuri kuko atawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariwe wenyene rudende gusa, Umuremyi w’inyegamo ry’iteka rihagije"
  23,117,"Nayo uwuyisenga hamwe n’Imana n’iyindi Mana nawe akaba atavyemezo afise kuri ibi, ntankeka iharurwa ryiwe riri ku Muremyi wiwe, mu vy’ukuri abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri ntaco bazoshikako"
  23,118,"Nawe nuvuge uti:- Muremyi wanje, nugirire ikigongwe uteko ubahe n’impuhwe zawe kuko ari wewe mwiza wizo mpuhwe"